$ PowerShell: the automatic variable $psItem ($_)

`$_` is an alias for `$psItem`.
-
The following two pipelines are equivalent:
gh|about-PowerShell|/language/variable/automatic/psItem/equivalency.ps1||

In a → Windows/PowerShell/language/statement/try-catch-finally[`catch` block], `$_` refers to the → Microsoft/dot-net/namespaces-classes/System/Exception[exception object] that caused the `catch` block to be invoked.

sa:
  Other → Windows/PowerShell/language/variable/automatic[automatic variables]
